<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title><para>A <tag>simplelist</tag> is a list of words or phrases. It
      offers a convenient alternative to the other list elements for inline
      content.</para>

      <refsection xml:id="dbreproc.simplelist"><info><title>Processing expectations</title></info>
        

        <para>Ironically, the processing expectations of a
        <tag>simplelist</tag> are quite complex. The value of the
        <tag class="attribute">type</tag> attribute determines if the
        list is presented inline, or in a row- or column-major table. In the
        table cases, the <tag class="attribute">columns</tag>
        attribute determines the number of columns in the table.</para>
</refsection>

